      "text": "A responsive table will display a horizontal scroll bar if the screen is too small to display the full content:",
      "html": "<p>A responsive table will display a horizontal scroll bar if the screen is too \nsmall to display the full content:</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "Add a container element (like <div>) with overflow-x:auto around the <table> element to make it responsive:",
      "html": "<p>Add a container element (like &lt;div&gt;) with <code>overflow-x:auto</code> around the &lt;table&gt; element to make it responsive:</p>"
